msgstr "Geen Dock-extensie actief"

msgid ""
"This page controls Ubuntu Dock / Dash to Dock or Dash to Panel. None of them "
"is enabled on this system."
msgstr ""
"Deze pagina beheert Ubuntu Dock, Dash to Dock of Dash to Panel. Geen van "
"deze is ingeschakeld op dit systeem."

