msgstr "(wachtwoord invoeren)"

msgid "Not changed (canceled or error)."
msgstr "Niet gewijzigd (geannuleerd of fout)."

msgid ""
"GTK apps and the cursor over the desktop change immediately. Already open "
"non-GTK apps (some terminals, Electron apps) show the old cursor until you "
"restart them."
msgstr ""
"GTK-apps en de cursor op het bureaublad veranderen direct. Al geopende "
"niet-GTK-apps (sommige terminals, Electron-apps) tonen de oude cursor totdat "
"je ze herstart."

